===Usage===
There are two variations on the stressed syllable in the genitive case. Generally, they are interchangeable. However, when used in the expressions {{RUchar|[[#Idioms|ни хуя́]]}} (ni khujá) and {{RUchar|[[#Idioms|до хуя́]]}} (do khujá), the last syllable should be stressed.

In the expressions {{RUchar|[[#Idioms|на́ хуй]]}} (ná khuj) and {{RUchar|[[#Idioms|по́ хую]]}} (pó khuju), the prepositions should be stressed.

